description:
Tried a Digital Detox. Still ended up with a 3 Day Lo-Grade Migraine. The “Real” World is so Messed Up - Literally in my Face. 😷Just going to get Groceries is infuriating. People wearing useless, dirty masks, handling items with filthy gloves, looking for arrows adhered to floor tiles - to tell them where to stand, which way to turn. Paranoid zombies feeding daily MSM sludge. They actually still believe that Shit? SMH.

Kinda tired of the mass willful ignorance, the smug virtue signalling, the insane double speak etc. (“Social” Distancing - WTF?) 

But how the Hell does one unplug from this “New Normal”...? Just isolate and pretend our Rights and Freedoms aren’t being messed with? Ignore the blatant Censorship of valid arguments that support and encourage a more Independent and Healthy population? Act like nothing’s Wrong with this whole situation? 

Just - Praying I don’t go Postal. .
.
